name: Adventure's of Túlio & Tiba #2
description: After a long struggle, Túlio & Tiba escaped from Douglas, the Demon. Túlio hides inside a tree, but Douglas manages to bite him. Tiba its accidentally glitched. "Adventure's of Túlio & Tiba" is my new series, produced in VR. The first page was created using Gravity Sketch + Blender. WiW (May 5, 2021).
